OL,3,C'Staggeringly stupid' man gave primary
OL,4,Cschool age children permanent tattoos
OL,6,FA man who gave permanent tattoos to
OL,7,Fthree primary age schoolchildren has
OL,8,Fbeen branded as "staggeringly stupid"
OL,9,Fas he was jailed for three years.
OL,11,FPatrick Coe's young victims had to
OL,12,Fundergo medical tests, have hepatitis
OL,13,Fand tetanus jabs and are now marked
OL,14,Fwith motifs on their bodies for life.
OL,16,FNewcastle Crown Court heard Coe, whose
OL,17,Faftercare comprised of cleaning with a
OL,18,Fbaby wipe, "didn't see anything wrong
OL,19,Fwith it".
