OL,3,C'Staggeringly stupid' man gave primary
OL,4,Cschool age children permanent tattoos
OL,6,FProsecutor Jessica Slaughter said the
OL,7,Fvictims were left anxious,
OL,8,Ftraumatised, scared about getting in
OL,9,Ftrouble, one said the pain was "seven
OL,10,Fout of ten" and another "hates" the
OL,11,Ftattoo.
OL,13,FCoe, 31, of Grafton House, Newcastle,
OL,14,Fadmitted three charges of child
OL,15,Fcruelty and has been jailed for three
OL,16,Fyears with a ten year restraining
OL,17,Forder.
