OL,3,C'Staggeringly stupid' man gave primary
OL,4,Cschool age children permanent tattoos
OL,6,FJudge Sarah Mallett said: "You
OL,7,Fsuggested they were temporary or would
OL,8,Fsignificantly fade and that is not
OL,9,Fthat case."
OL,11,FThe judge said the children were left
OL,12,Fwith "cosmetic disfigurement" which is
OL,13,Fa permanent injury and added: "The
OL,14,Ftattoos are small but clearly visible
OL,15,Fand a permanent reminder of you and
OL,16,Fthis.
OL,18,F"This was a staggeringly stupid and
OL,19,Ffoolish thing to do and also a very
OL,20,Fharmful thing to do."
