OL,3,C'Staggeringly stupid' man gave primary
OL,4,Cschool age children permanent tattoos
OL,6,FBrian Hegarty, defending, said:
OL,7,F"There's little I can do to mitigate
OL,8,Fthe stupidity of his actions.
OL,10,F"It is frankly staggering and defies
OL,11,Fbelief he could be so foolish.
OL,13,F"He has come to appreciate just how
OL,14,Fill-judged his actions have been and
OL,15,Facknowledges how wrong he was.
OL,17,F"He is deeply remorseful he has caused
OL,18,Fany pain at all to the children."
